# correlated contributors: joining every row against a shared one-row table
# makes each provenance a conjunction (row AND switch), no longer a set of
# independent literals, so the worlds combine in the non-certified m-semiring.
# sum(x) > sum(y) now also needs the switch present: the 0.25 above times
# P(switch) = 0.5.
